    <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
      <div class="z-10 relative">
        <Image
          src={SolpakaImage}
          alt="Solpaka logo"
          width={650}
          class="z-10 float"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="text-white">
        SOLPAKA is a community-driven token aiming to build a strong and vibrant
        community in the Solana ecosystem. SOLPAKA is a meme coin but it does
        not stop it from being one of the most loved and admired tokens on
        Solana. SOLPAKA aims to build a strong foundation of open-minded people
        and continue building and investing in new, long-term projects.
      </p>
    </div>
